<p>plentymarkets generates all emails based on templates. For the beginning, we recommend setting up the email templates listed in <a href="#table-email-templates">Table 4</a>. Go to <strong>System » System settings » Client » Select client » Email » Templates</strong> to create email templates.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can adapt all email templates to your individual needs. Go to the chapter <a href="/en/quick-start/quick-start-initial-settings#600">Example: Customising the email template</a> further down on this page of the manual, you find an example how to customise the email template <strong>Online store: confirmation of store order</strong>.</p>
